{"tid":750701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真］係香港揸電單車危唔危險？","createTime":"2018-07-21T06:39:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T07:58:49.000Z","uid":178645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a2744635ba52238796244da33ca0fddeaa49239b","tid":750701,"uid":178645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:39:15.000Z","msg":"本人住係新界都幾入 <br />\n平時就係港島返工都要坐個半鐘車<br />\n最近諗緊如果考左電單車會唔會方便好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae4a0ec84ca22e7f12f4212c8fece55996d594c","tid":750701,"uid":21424,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:41:13.000Z","msg":"下世小心D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16721e6ddbe10fe4781b219d9f7a5facd1b99ce0","tid":750701,"uid":4826,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:42:39.000Z","msg":"太多女司機，你話呢"},{"pid":"97c1839111da837b8e27b7c04fb5a58d7c63d7be","tid":750701,"uid":178645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aae4a0ec84ca22e7f12f4212c8fece55996d594c","tid":750701,"uid":21424,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:41:13.000Z","msg":"下世小心D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:44:01.000Z","msg":"有無咁誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7762482ac4828e54534432241997dacb36e0aec","tid":750701,"uid":178645,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"16721e6ddbe10fe4781b219d9f7a5facd1b99ce0","tid":750701,"uid":4826,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:42:39.000Z","msg":"太多女司機，你話呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:45:08.000Z","msg":"平時朝早打個飛機先返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=